{
    "poem_title": "Au Lecteur",
    "author": "Charles Baudelaire",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1857-1861",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "La sottise, l’erreur, le péché, la lésine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Occupent nos esprits et travaillent nos corps,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Et nous alimentons nos aimables remords,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Comme les mendiants nourrissent leur vermine.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La sottise, l’erreur, le péché, la lésine,\nOccupent nos esprits et travaillent nos corps,\nEt nous alimentons nos aimables remords,\nComme les mendiants nourrissent leur vermine."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Nos péchés sont têtus, nos repentirs sont lâches ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Nous nous faisons payer grassement nos aveux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et nous rentrons gaîment dans le chemin bourbeux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Croyant par de vils pleurs laver toutes nos taches.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nos péchés sont têtus, nos repentirs sont lâches ;\nNous nous faisons payer grassement nos aveux,\nEt nous rentrons gaîment dans le chemin bourbeux,\nCroyant par de vils pleurs laver toutes nos taches."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Sur l’oreiller du mal c’est Satan Trismégiste",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Qui berce longuement notre esprit enchanté,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Et le riche métal de notre volonté",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Est tout vaporisé par ce savant chimiste.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sur l’oreiller du mal c’est Satan Trismégiste\nQui berce longuement notre esprit enchanté,\nEt le riche métal de notre volonté\nEst tout vaporisé par ce savant chimiste."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "C’est le Diable qui tient les fils qui nous remuent !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Aux objets répugnants nous trouvons des appas ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Chaque jour vers l’Enfer nous descendons d’un pas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Sans horreur, à travers des ténèbres qui puent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’est le Diable qui tient les fils qui nous remuent !\nAux objets répugnants nous trouvons des appas ;\nChaque jour vers l’Enfer nous descendons d’un pas,\nSans horreur, à travers des ténèbres qui puent."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi qu’un débauché pauvre qui baise et mange",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Le sein martyrisé d’une antique catin,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Nous volons au passage un plaisir clandestin",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Que nous pressons bien fort comme une vieille orange.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ainsi qu’un débauché pauvre qui baise et mange\nLe sein martyrisé d’une antique catin,\nNous volons au passage un plaisir clandestin\nQue nous pressons bien fort comme une vieille orange."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Serré, fourmillant, comme un million d’helminthes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Dans nos cerveaux ribote un peuple de Démons,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Et, quand nous respirons, la Mort dans nos poumons",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Descend, fleuve invisible, avec de sourdes plaintes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Serré, fourmillant, comme un million d’helminthes,\nDans nos cerveaux ribote un peuple de Démons,\nEt, quand nous respirons, la Mort dans nos poumons\nDescend, fleuve invisible, avec de sourdes plaintes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Si le viol, le poison, le poignard, l’incendie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "N’ont pas encor brodé de leurs plaisants dessins",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Le canevas banal de nos piteux destins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "C’est que notre âme, hélas ! n’est pas assez hardie.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Si le viol, le poison, le poignard, l’incendie,\nN’ont pas encor brodé de leurs plaisants dessins\nLe canevas banal de nos piteux destins,\nC’est que notre âme, hélas ! n’est pas assez hardie."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Mais parmi les chacals, les panthères, les lices,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Les singes, les scorpions, les vautours, les serpents,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Les monstres glapissants, hurlants, grognants, rampants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Dans la ménagerie infâme de nos vices,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais parmi les chacals, les panthères, les lices,\nLes singes, les scorpions, les vautours, les serpents,\nLes monstres glapissants, hurlants, grognants, rampants,\nDans la ménagerie infâme de nos vices,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Il en est un plus laid, plus méchant, plus immonde !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Quoiqu’il ne pousse ni grands gestes ni grands cris,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Il ferait volontiers de la terre un débris",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Et dans un bâillement avalerait le monde ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il en est un plus laid, plus méchant, plus immonde !\nQuoiqu’il ne pousse ni grands gestes ni grands cris,\nIl ferait volontiers de la terre un débris\nEt dans un bâillement avalerait le monde ;"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "C’est l’Ennui ! — L’œil chargé d’un pleur involontaire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Il rêve d’échafauds en fumant son houka.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Tu le connais, lecteur, ce monstre délicat,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "— Hypocrite lecteur, — mon semblable, — mon frère !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’est l’Ennui ! — L’œil chargé d’un pleur involontaire,\nIl rêve d’échafauds en fumant son houka.\nTu le connais, lecteur, ce monstre délicat,\n— Hypocrite lecteur, — mon semblable, — mon frère !"
        }
    ],
    "corpus": "mel"
